title: Seashell Boy
description: Kang Doo-sik goes back to the restaurant to pay money after trying to eat without paying. However, he saw something that he shouldn’t see there…Watch the interaction between Kang Doo-sik, who is polite, and Jin Juha, who is tough but honest to discover the secret lay beneath. Will Doosik finds out what kind of a person Jin Juha is?!
